#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Help"
msgstr "ऑनलाइन सहायता"

#. Tag: date
#: index.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "2018-04-01"
msgstr "२०१८-०४-०१"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: index.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applications 18.04"
msgstr "अनुप्रयोगाः १८.०४"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page, you can find different ways to find online help and additional "
"information provided by the &kde; community."
msgstr "अस्मिन् पृष्ठे भवन्तः &kde; समुदाय।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; UserBase"
msgstr "&कुत्र; UserBase इति"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/"
"An_introduction_to_KDE\">An Introduction to &kde;</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/"
"An_introduction_to_KDE\">&kde;</ulink> इत्यस्य परिचयः&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Learn more about the <ulink url=\"https://kde.org/community/whatiskde/\"> "
"&kde; community and its software</ulink> and find information to help you "
"get started. Also, discover what <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/"
"Special:myLanguage/Welcome_to_KDE_UserBase\"> UserBase</ulink> is and how it "
"can help you."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://kde.org/community/whatiskde/\"> &kde; समुदायः तस्य "
"सॉफ्टवेयर</ulink> च तथा च भवतः आरम्भे सहायकं सूचनां अन्वेष्टुम्। अपि च, <ulink url="
"\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Welcome_to_KDE_UserBase\"> "
"UserBase</ulink> इति किम्, कथं च भवतः सहायतां कर्तुं शक्नोति इति अन्वेष्टुम् ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Getting_Help"
"\">Getting Help</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/सहायता_प्राप्तिः"
"\">सहायतां प्राप्तुं</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Need some help? Here are some suggested places where you can get help with "
"problems, as well some hints on how to improve the quality of answers you "
"receive."
msgstr ""
"किञ्चित् साहाय्यस्य आवश्यकता अस्ति वा ? अत्र केचन सुझाताः स्थानानि सन्ति यत्र भवन्तः "
"समस्यासु सहायतां प्राप्तुं शक्नुवन्ति, तथैव भवन्तः प्राप्तानां उत्तराणां गुणवत्तां कथं सुधारयितुम् "
"अर्हन्ति इति केचन संकेताः अपि सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Applications"
"\">Applications</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Applications"
"\">अनुप्रयोग</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Discover the wide variety of applications from the &kde; Community, and find "
"out what program suits your needs and preferences."
msgstr ""
"&kde; समुदायः, तथा च ज्ञातव्यं यत् कोऽपि कार्यक्रमः भवतः आवश्यकतानां प्राधान्यानां च "
"अनुकूलः अस्ति।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Tutorials"
"\">Tutorials</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Tutorials"
"\">पाठ्यक्रमाः</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How-To's, Tips &amp; Tricks that can help make your &kde; software "
"experience more enjoyable and productive."
msgstr ""
"How-To's, युक्तयः &amp; युक्तयः ये भवतः &kde; सॉफ्टवेयर अनुभवः अधिकं आनन्ददायकः "
"उत्पादकः च।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Forum"
msgstr "&कुत्र; मञ्चः"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/\">&kde; Community Forums</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/\">&kde; सामुदायिकमञ्चाः</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kde; Forums offer users, developers and people interested in &kde; a "
"place to help each other, discuss &kde;-related topics and exchange ideas. "
"You can find <ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/viewforum.php?f=14/"
"\">Tutorials &amp; Tips</ulink> in the forum."
msgstr ""
"इति &kde; मञ्चाः उपयोक्तृभ्यः, विकासकान्, &kde; परस्परं साहाय्यं कर्तुं, &kde;-"
"सम्बद्धविषयेषु चर्चां कर्तुं, विचाराणां आदानप्रदानं कर्तुं च स्थानम्। भवन्तः <ulink url="
"\"https://forum.kde.org/viewforum.php?f=14/\">पाठ्यक्रमाः &amp; मञ्चे युक्तयः</"
"ulink> इति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Techbase"
msgstr "&कुत्र; टेक्बेस"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "<ulink url=\"https://techbase.kde.org/\">&kde; Techbase</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<ulink url=\"https://techbase.kde.org/\">&kde; टेक्बेस्</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Information for developers and help to set up a &kde; development "
"environment."
msgstr "विकासकानां कृते सूचना तथा च &kde; विकास वातावरण।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Documentation"
msgstr "&kde; दस्तावेजीकरणम्"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; Documentation site</ulink>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; प्रलेखनस्थल</ulink>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page holds the complete &kde; User Documentation in over 25 languages "
"for the released and the development version of &kde-frameworks;, &plasma-"
"workspaces; and &applications;."
msgstr ""
"अस्मिन् पृष्ठे सम्पूर्णं &kde; &kde-frameworks;, &plasma-workspaces; तथा &अनुप्रयोगाः;।"
